                  </persName>
            . Q. When did you loose these things - A. On the 5th of July, I lost them out of a<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181107100046"></xptr>box which was not locked, out of my own bed room. The prisoner lodged in my house.</p>
               <p>Q. Did you ever find your property - A. Yes, I charged the constable with her, she owned where she had pawned the goods; she gave one duplicate and that her mother with the other two.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18110710-78-person755">
                  JEREMIAH 
                  LEWIS
               <interp inst="t18110710-78-person755" type="surname" value="LEWIS"></interp>
