                     <interp inst="t18110710-78-person755" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker, I live with Mr. Killingworth, 200, Brick-lane. I took in pawn a petticoat of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18110710-78-person756">
                  THOMAS 
                  MANNING
               <interp inst="t18110710-78-person756" type="surname" value="MANNING"></interp>
